ed="T" n="0716c26"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0716c25"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000034754">益州多寶寺</placeName><persName key="A008882">道因</persName>傳<ptr target="#n25"/>（<persName key="A005407">嵩公</persName> <persName key="A004354">寶暹</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0716c26"/><persName key="A008882">釋道因</persName>，姓<name>侯</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000024797">濮陽</placeName>人也。稟祜居醇<ptr type="glossary" target="#g276"/>，含章<ptr type="glossary" target="#g277"/><lb
ed="T" n="0716c27"/>縱哲，<date key="j19358231937649" notBefore-iso="+0588-01-01" notAfter-iso="+0592-12-31">覃訏之歲</date><ptr type="glossary" target="#g278"/>，粹<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>釆</sic><corr>采</corr></choice><ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g279"/>多奇，<date key="j19376501940205" notAfter-iso="+0599-12-31" notBefore-iso="+0593-01-01">髫齓之辰</date><ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g280"/>，殊姿特<lb
ed="T" n="0716c28"/>茂。孝愛之節，慈順之風，率志于斯，因心<ptr type="glossary" target="#g281"/>以<lb
ed="T" n="0716c29"/>極。年甫<date key="j19376521938016" from-iso="+0593-01-03" to-iso="+0594-01-02">七歲</date>，丁于內艱<ptr type="glossary" target="#g282"/>，嗌粒絕漿，殆乎滅<pb ed="T" n="0717a" xml:id="T50.2061.0717a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0717a01"/>性<ptr type="glossary" target="#g283"/>。成人<ptr type="glossary" target="#g284"/>之德，見稱州里。<date key="j19387451939110" from-iso="+0596-01-01" to-iso="+0596-12-31">免喪</date><ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g285"/>之後，思酬<lb
ed="T" n="0717a02"/>罔極<ptr type="glossary" target="#g286"/>，出家之志，人莫我移。便詣<placeName key="PL000000020295">靈巖寺</placeName>求<lb
ed="T" n="0717a03"/>師誦習，曾不浹旬<ptr type="glossary" target="#g287"/>，通《涅槃經》二帙<ptr target="#n299"/>，舉眾驚<lb
ed="T" n="0717a04"/>駭，謂為神童。落髮已來，砥礪其行，揣摩《義<lb
ed="T" n="0717a05"/>章》<ptr target="#n288"/>，即講《涅槃》，宿齒名流，咸所歎服。</p><p>及升上<lb
ed="T" n="0717a06"/>品<ptr type="glossary" target="#g289"/>，旋學律儀<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g290"/>，又於<placeName key="PL000000009517">彭城</placeName><persName key="A005407">嵩<roleName>法師</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n26"/>所傳《攝大<lb
ed="T" n="0717a07"/>乘》<ptr target="#n27"/>。<persName key="A005407">嵩<roleName>公</roleName></persName>懿德玄猷，蘭薰月映，門徒學侶，魚貫<lb
ed="T" n="0717a08"/>鳧趨，講室談筵，為之囂隘。遂依科戒而為<lb
ed="T" n="0717a09"/>節文<ptr type="glossary" target="#g291"/>，年少沙門且令習律，曉《四分》<ptr target="#n28"/>者，方許<lb
ed="T" n="0717a10"/>入聽。<persName key="A008882">因</persName>夏臘雖幼，業行<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g292"/>攸高，獨於眾中，逈<lb
ed="T" n="0717a11"/>見推揖，每敷《攝論》，即令覆講。</p><p>後隱<placeName key="PL000000021580">泰嶽</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0717a12"/>凡經四秋。將詣<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛中</placeName>，屬昏<anchor xml:id="beg0717sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>李</sic><corr>季</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0717sgsz1"/>陵夷，法<anchor xml:id="beg0717001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>綱</sic><corr>網</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0717001"/><lb
ed="T" n="0717a13"/>嚴峻，僧無徒侶，弗許遊方<ptr target="#n293"/>。於是杖錫出<lb
ed="T" n="0717a14"/>山，孑焉超邁<ptr target="#n294"/>，恐<anchor xml:id="beg0717sgsz2"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>羅</sic><corr>罹</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0717sgsz2"/>刑憲，靜念<persName key="A002803">觀音</persName>。少選之<lb
ed="T" n="0717a15"/>間，有僧歘<ptr type="glossary" target="#g295"/>至，皓然白首，請與偕行。迨至<placeName key="PL000000023590">銅<lb
ed="T" n="0717a16"/>街</placeName>，暨於金地，俯仰之際，莫知所在。咸謂<persName key="A002799">善<lb
ed="T" n="0717a17"/>逝</persName>之力<ptr target="#n29"/>，有感斯見。未幾，<persName key="A008882">因</persName>避難<placeName key="PL000000034650">三蜀</placeName>，居于<lb
ed="T" n="0717a18"/><placeName key="PL000000034754">多寶寺</placeName>。好事者素聞道譽，乃命開筵《攝論》、《維<lb
ed="T" n="0717a19"/>摩》，聽者千數。</p><p>時有<persName key="A004354">寶暹<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>，<placeName key="PL000000010400">東海</placeName>人也，殖<lb
ed="T" n="0717a20"/>藝該洽，尤善大乘，昔在<date from-iso="+0581-03-06" key="j19333311946884" to-iso="+0618-04-15"><name>隋</name>朝</date>，英塵久播，學<lb
ed="T" n="0717a21"/>徒來請，接武<ptr type="glossary" target="#g296"/>磨肩。<persName key="A004354">暹公</persName>傲爾其間，仰之彌<lb
ed="T" n="0717a22"/>峻，每至<persName key="A008882">因</persName>之論席，肅然改容，沈吟久之，方<lb
ed="T" n="0717a23"/>用酬遣。<persName key="A008882">因</persName>抗音<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g297"/>馳辯，雷驚波注，盡妙窮微，<lb
ed="T" n="0717a24"/>藏牙折角<ptr type="glossary" target="#g298"/>。<placeName key="PL000000034805">益州</placeName>總管鄧國公<persName key="A008885">竇璡</persName>、行臺左僕<lb
ed="T" n="0717a25"/>射<anchor xml:id="beg0717002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>替</sic><corr>賛</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0717002"/>國公<persName key="A005740">竇軌</persName><ptr target="#n239"/>、長史申國公<persName key="A008886">高士廉</persName>、范陽公<lb
ed="T" n="0717a26"/><persName key="A008888">盧承慶</persName>，及前後首僚，西南嶽牧，並國華朝秀，<lb
ed="T" n="0717a27"/>重望崇班<ptr type="glossary" target="#g299"/>，共籍芳聲，俱申虔仰。乃於<placeName key="PL000000035021">彭門<lb
ed="T" n="0717a28"/>山寺</placeName>習道安居。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000035021">此寺</ref>往經廢毀，院宇凋弊，<persName key="A008882">因</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0717a29"/>慨然構懷，專事營緝，未移再稔，蔚成淨場。<pb ed="T" n="0717b" xml:id="T50.2061.0717b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0717b01"/>又以九部<ptr type="glossary" target="#g300"/>微言，三界<ptr type="glossary" target="#g301"/>式仰，緬惟法盡，將翳<lb
ed="T" n="0717b02"/><placeName key="PL000000055445">龍宮</placeName>。遂於<ref target="#PL000000035021" type="place">寺</ref>之北巖，刻書經典，窮多羅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g302"/>之<lb
ed="T" n="0717b03"/>祕袠，盡毘尼之正文。縱<persName key="A002433">堯</persName>世之洪水襄陵，<lb
ed="T" n="0717b04"/>任<persName key="A019724">趙簡</persName>之北山燎狩<ptr target="#n36"/>，必無他慮，與劫<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g303"/>齊休。<lb
ed="T" n="0717b05"/></p><p>既而清猷遠暢，峻業遐昭。遂簡<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g304"/>宸衷，乃紆天<lb
ed="T" n="0717b06"/>綍<ptr type="glossary" target="#g305"/>，追赴<placeName key="PL000000042189">京邑</placeName>，止<placeName key="PL000000042410">大慈恩寺</placeName>，與<persName key="A000294">玄奘<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>翻<lb
ed="T" n="0717b07"/>譯校定<name>梵</name>本，兼充證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/>。<persName key="A000294">奘師</persName>偏獎賞之，每<lb
ed="T" n="0717b08"/>有難文，同加參酌，新翻弗墜，<persName key="A008882">因</persName>有力焉。<placeName key="PL000000042131">慧<lb
ed="T" n="0717b09"/>日寺</placeName>主<persName key="A008889"><anchor xml:id="beg0717sgsz3"/>楷<anchor xml:id="end0717sgsz3"/><roleName>法師</roleName></persName>者，聰爽溫贍<ptr type="glossary" target="#g306"/>，聲藹鴻都<ptr type="glossary" target="#g307"/>，首建<lb
ed="T" n="0717b10"/>法筵，請開奧義。<ref target="#PL000000042189" type="place">帝城</ref>緇俗，具來諮稟，欣焉<lb
ed="T" n="0717b11"/>相顧，得所未聞。<persName key="A008882">因</persName>研幾史籍，尤好《老》、《莊》，<lb
ed="T" n="0717b12"/>咀其菁華，含其腴潤，包四始<ptr type="glossary" target="#g63"/>於風律<ptr type="glossary" target="#g308"/>，綜五<lb
ed="T" n="0717b13"/>聲於文緒，故所講訓，內外該通。其專業者，<lb
ed="T" n="0717b14"/>《涅槃華嚴》、《大品》<ptr target="#n37"/>、《維摩》、《法華》、《楞伽》<ptr target="#n52"/>等經，《十地》<ptr target="#n53"/>、《地持》<ptr target="#n54"/>、<lb
ed="T" n="0717b15"/>《毘曇》、《智度》<ptr target="#n55"/>、《攝大乘》、《對法》<ptr target="#n61"/>、《佛地》<ptr target="#n63"/>等論，及《四分》<ptr target="#n70"/>等<lb
ed="T" n="0717b16"/>律。其《攝論》、《維摩》仍著章疏。</p><p>已而能事畢矣，<lb
ed="T" n="0717b17"/>示疾終于<placeName key="PL000000042131">長安慧日寺</placeName>，則<date key="j19615001961500" when-iso="+0658-04-21"><name>顯慶</name>三年三月十<lb
ed="T" n="0717b18"/>一日</date>也，春秋七十二。越<date from-iso="+0659-02-01" key="j19617861961814" to-iso="+0659-03-01">明年正月</date>，旋神座于<lb
ed="T" n="0717b19"/><placeName key="PL000000034805">益部</placeName>，<date key="j19618221961822" when-iso="+0659-03-09">二月八日</date>窆于<placeName key="PL000000035021">彭門光化寺</placeName>石經之側。<lb
ed="T" n="0717b20"/>道俗送葬，數有數千。弟子<persName key="A008890">玄<anchor xml:id="beg0717sgsz4"/>凝<anchor xml:id="end0717sgsz4"/></persName>等嗣其香<lb
ed="T" n="0717b21"/>火。至<date notBefore-iso="+0661-04-08" key="j19625831963615" notAfter-iso="+0664-02-04"><name>龍朔</name>中</date>，中臺司藩大夫<persName key="A008892">李儼</persName>製碑，<persName key="A008893">歐陽<lb
ed="T" n="0717b22"/>通</persName>書焉。</p>
